===Idiom===
'''[[不可]][[思]][[议]]'''

# mysterious; unimaginable; incomprehensible
#: ''[[这]][[件]][[事]][[听]][[起]][[来]][[简直]]'''不可思议'''。''
#: ''From the sound of it, this is something that is simply '''incomprehensible'''.''

